snippet.textDisplay: Fuckin' A!! Definitely one of my favs from this season. Paar Channa De is my absolute fav though. I love Noori so much!! Love these two singers as well. The girl has such a rustic voice. The best thing abt Pakistani music is how you guys incorporate cultural/ethnic/folksy stuff and combine it with rock n roll. Much love from across the border 🇮🇳 I wish I could go to Lahore someday. It's so close to Delhi. Barely 400-500 km away. Closer than so many other regions of India itself. Yet it's so difficult and expensive to go to Pakistan. It's literally the next city after Amritsar yet we can't just go on a road trip there. Breaks my heart 😫
